node.text:
If you truly want to be great, spend every waking hour helping others to be great first.🔥🤔💯😏

So many people want to be Kings and Queens yet they do not know how to be Servants. And they will fail because they desire power but not responsibility. Even worse, they want power for themselves and not for the good of others. This attitude is not only arrogant but will surely lead to destruction.

node.text:
9 of the BEST Lessons for Entrepreneurs...⁣⁣
⁣⁣
1. Face your fear of failure, Let it be okay 👌🏾 to fail and let it be a driving force ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
2. Find mentors to help guide your growth - cut your learning curve through calls, conferences, and reaching out to mentors direct⁣⁣
⁣⁣
3. Invest profits back into your business - invest $ 💰back into yourself and your business directly. Invest now to reap rewards later! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
4. Build a great team and culture - encourage growth and help people build their vision for their own growth and goals as well as the companies! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
5. It’s not all about the money! - catch onto a bigger mission. You must Sometimes lose and learn first before you earn anyways. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
6. Keep doubts to yourself - It’s ok to be vulnerable and real but don’t spread doubts to your team. Stay strong and speak abundantly! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
7. Being a leader is difficult but worth it! Look at stepping into a leadership position no matter how uncomfortable it feels. It pays to step up and it feels great to help others! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
8. Keep being innovative - always look for new strategies and tactics that will help your business progress and grow. Creativity and innovation creates momentum! ⁣⁣
⁣
9. Notice your AHA moment. When your vision and mission becomes clear that is when you will start to see struggles turn into successes! ⁣
⁣
Cheers! If you are with me drop a 🥂

node.text:
If you want to hit your income goals, break your goal into what I call a DIG.

A Daily Income Goal.

Say you want to hit your first $5K month online.

To get there, you’ll need to make $166.67 per day.

That doesn’t sound like much does it?

If you want to hit $10K per month, then that number becomes $333.33.

Remember, you’re in the business of making money today.

If you don’t hit your daily income goals you won’t hit your monthly income goals.

What’s your daily income goal?
